{"tid":1999081,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中国恐嚇荷蘭可停止醫護物資援助，全因質易處加入「台北」兩字","createTime":"2020-05-03T02:22:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-13T08:12:16.000Z","uid":36073,"like":292,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":119,"replies":[{"pid":"4d9c3b039ca4a0f11c5532326b184e3274670097","tid":1999081,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T02:22:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://tnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw/photos/2020/04/30/1588213965-5eaa38cdd7c5a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw%2Fphotos%2F2020%2F04%2F30%2F1588213965-5eaa38cdd7c5a.jpg&h=36d4726c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nOn Tuesday (April 28), The Netherlands Trade and Investment Office changed its name to &ldquo;Netherlands Office Taipei,&quot; with Dutch representative in Taipei Guy Wittich referring to the new moniker as &quot;little bit less, but a lot more.&quot; In a video clip that was released on Monday evening but later taken down, Wittich elaborated that the name had been changed and simplified because of an expansion of activities in many new areas between the two countries.<br />\n<br />\nWittich said that the terms &quot;trade and investment&quot; had been taken out, as the scope of cooperation between the two countries had increased. Over the past eight years, the Australian, British, Japanese, and Polish representative offices have similarly simplified the names of their de facto embassies in Taiwan.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://tnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw/photos/2020/04/28/1588056466-5ea7d1927c18e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftnimage.s3.hicloud.net.tw%2Fphotos%2F2020%2F04%2F28%2F1588056466-5ea7d1927c18e.png&h=1006b665&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">In response, the Chinese embassy in the European country on Tuesday lodged &quot;solemn representations&quot; and demanded a &quot;clarification&quot; of the name change from the Dutch government. The embassy claimed that the name change &quot;concerns China's core interests&quot; and reminded the Netherlands to dutifully adhere to its &quot;one China principle.&quot;</span><br />\n<br />\nChina threatens to halt medical supplies after Netherlands changes Taiwan rep office name<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3925556?fbclid=IwAR1BilE_H69iLtOygYHN9NrjrWE7-5uHHxwWffHBN38Dm4lLlrVCkPjEgUw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.taiwannews.com.tw%2Fen%2Fnews%2F3925556%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1BilE_H69iLtOygYHN9NrjrWE7-5uHHxwWffHBN38Dm4lLlrVCkPjEgUw&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=2fea2bfd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.taiwannews.com.tw/en/news/3925556?fbclid=IwAR1BilE_H69iLtOygYHN9NrjrWE7-5uHHxwWffHBN38Dm4lLlrVCkPjEgUw</a>"},{"pid":"aada310a8346e3951b2100dc7f8393f4eeae7370","tid":1999081,"uid":130797,"like":189,"dislike":1,"score":188,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T02:27:14.000Z","msg":"加得上去就表示唔撚驚你啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed83b83e2a7f900fb61cd151ab68e9798e5034f1","tid":1999081,"uid":48040,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T02:27:45.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FC7YbpoujZlw&d=5G%2Bx0n%2BFJXS0hP%2BJIuhjgg8%2Bx5Wy5jX%2Bp0OgAvZs4CE%3D&h=30e09871\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/C7YbpoujZlw</a>"},{"pid":"9c35d3341928ed68a6199833fe72bbb9de75a17f","tid":1999081,"uid":143241,"like":46,"dislike":0,"score":46,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T02:28:34.000Z","msg":"黑社會國家"},{"pid":"b35714ebfb3d78f63e863c55fed3fff6e569eac2","tid":1999081,"uid":22624,"like":81,"dislike":0,"score":81,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-03T02:28:49.000Z","msg":"雜種張相揀得幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8908fb009e33fd4bc35cca7c03aab2c4d2d3e7d8","tid":1999081,"uid":305083,"like":4